:: Compact Nock core for the decrement arm in examples/dec.hoon.
:: Brackets use the Nock convention [a b c] == [a [b c]].
::
:: dec-loop-battery
[6 [5 [4 0 7] 0 6] [0 7] 9 2 10 [3 [0 6] 4 0 7] 0 1]
::
:: dec-gate-battery
[9 2 [1 6 [5 [4 0 7] 0 6] [0 7] 9 2 10 [3 [0 6] 4 0 7] 0 1] [0 3] 1 0]
::
:: dec-core-3
[[9 2 [1 6 [5 [4 0 7] 0 6] [0 7] 9 2 10 [3 [0 6] 4 0 7] 0 1] [0 3] 1 0] 3]
::
:: dec-call
[9 2 0 1]
